00:21:06,708 --> 00:21:08,073
<font color="#787878">Wait.</font>

213
00:21:08,176 --> 00:21:10,303
<font color="#787878">There's something you need to see first.</font>

214
00:21:10,846 --> 00:21:12,006
<font color="#787878">I need to see Bella.</font>

215
00:21:12,280 --> 00:21:13,611
<font color="#787878">Look,</font>

216
00:21:14,516 --> 00:21:17,679
<font color="#787878">in order for Bella to get better, she had to</font>

