00:23:07,362 --> 00:23:09,990
<font color="#787878">Maybe a tad slower. Hmm.</font>

251
00:23:10,098 --> 00:23:11,531
<font color="#787878">And blink at least three times a minute.</font>

252
00:23:15,237 --> 00:23:16,204
<font color="#787878">Good.</font>

253
