<font color="#787878">For a cartoon character.</font>

254
00:23:19,574 --> 00:23:21,633
<font color="#787878">Hold your breath. It will help with the thirst.</font>

255
00:23:22,878 --> 00:23:25,847
<font color="#787878">Just don't forget to move your shoulders so it looks like 
