294
00:26:33,835 --> 00:26:35,427
<font color="#787878">And I don't need to know this?</font>

295
00:26:36,438 --> 00:26:37,405
<font color="#787878">No.</font>

296
00:26:37,972 --> 00:26:39,234
<font color="#787878">Really, you don't.</font>

297
00:26:44,913 --> 00:26:46,073
<font color="#787878">Well....</font>

298
00:26:48,149 --> 00:26:49,582
<font color="#787878">Not gonna lose you again.</font>

299
00:26:51,119 --> 00:26:52,450
<font color="#787878">I can't.</font>

300
00:26:54,522 --> 00:26:55,750
<font color="#787878">Then you won't.</font>

301
00:26:58,493 --> 00:26:59,585
<font color="#787878">I promise.</font>

302
00:27:16,444 --> 00:27:17,775
<font color="#787878">I missed you, Bells.</font>

303
00:27:19,614 --> 00:27:20,638
<font color="#787878">So much.</font>

304
00:27:23,118 --> 00:27:24,745
<font color="#787878">I missed you, Dad.</font>

305
00:27:29,691 --> 00:27:30,658
<font color="#787878">Charlie.</font>

306
00:27:33,895 --> 00:27:35,192
<font color="#787878">This is Renesmee.</font>

307
00:27:40,668 --> 00:27:41,726
<font color="#787878">Your niece?</font>

308
00:27:43,872 --> 00:27:44,998
<font color="#787878">Our daughter.</font>

309
00:27:49,377 --> 00:27:50,344
<font color="#787878">Right.</font>

310
00:27:50,845 --> 00:27:52,005
<font color="#787878">The adoption.</font>

