00:27:58,219 --> 00:27:59,516
<font color="#787878">Renee-semee?</font>

312
00:28:03,558 --> 00:28:05,082
<font color="#787878">She's got your eyes, Bella.</font>

313
00:28:13,434 --> 00:28:15,265
<font color="#787878">Need to know, I guess.</font>

314
00:28:30,819 --> 00:28:31,945
<font color="#c800b0">JASPER:</font> <font color="#787878">Well done, Bella.</font>

315
00:28:32,320 --> 00:28:34,515
<font color="#787878">Never seen a newborn
show that kind of restraint.</font>

316
00:28:35,056 --> 00:28:37,388
<font color="#787878">I'm not sure she is a newborn.</font>

317
00:28:37,826 --> 00:28:39,623
<font color="#787878">She's so tame.</font>

