<font color="#c800b0">(APPLAUDING)</font>

327
00:29:21,569 --> 00:29:22,593
<font color="#787878">Did you see that?</font>

328
00:29:27,542 --> 00:29:28,873
<font color="#c800b0">(ALL CHUCKLING)</font>

