00:29:28,977 --> 00:29:30,274
<font color="#787878">Thank you.</font>

330
00:29:53,134 --> 00:29:55,102
<font color="#c800b0">BELLA:</font> <font color="#787878">My time as a human was over.</font>

331
00:29:56,804 --> 00:29:58,772
<font color="#787878">But I never felt more alive.</font>

332
00:30:00,909 --> 00:30:02,536
<font color="#787878">I was born to be a vampire.</font>

