335
00:30:26,734 --> 00:30:28,201
<font color="#787878">Though they'd want proof eventually.</font>

336
00:30:32,573 --> 00:30:33,938
<font color="#787878">It seemed we had only one enemy left.</font>

337
00:30:35,510 --> 00:30:36,477
<font color="#787878">Time.</font>

