340
00:30:48,823 --> 00:30:50,688
<font color="#787878">It just made every moment more precious.</font>

341
00:30:51,359 --> 00:30:52,826
<font color="#c800b0">RENESMEE:</font> <font color="#787878">Look, a snowflake.</font>

342
00:30:53,695 --> 00:30:54,719
<font color="#787878">It's beautiful.</font>

