00:30:55,563 --> 00:30:56,757
<font color="#787878">Why don't you go get another one?</font>

344
00:31:01,936 --> 00:31:04,063
<font color="#787878">Edward thinks that
we'll find answers in Brazil.</font>

345
00:31:05,840 --> 00:31:07,705
<font color="#787878">There are tribes there
that might know something.</font>

346
00:31:24,625 --> 00:31:25,649
<font color="#c800b0">RENESMEE:</font> <font color="#787878">Who was that?</font>

347
00:31:26,794 --> 00:31:29,228
<font color="#787878">I think that's our cousin from Denali.</font>

