00:33:37,258 --> 00:33:38,885
<font color="#787878">The Cullens....</font>

363
00:33:39,927 --> 00:33:42,896
<font color="#787878">They've done something terrible.</font>

364
00:33:45,199 --> 00:33:47,463
<font color="#787878">Allow me, my dear.</font>

365
00:34:06,320 --> 00:34:07,548
<font color="#787878">Oh, my.</font>

