368
00:34:43,090 --> 00:34:44,148
<font color="#787878">The Volturi.</font>

369
00:34:45,793 --> 00:34:46,919
<font color="#787878">They're coming for us.</font>

370
00:34:47,295 --> 00:34:51,925
<font color="#787878">Aro, Caius, Marcus, the Guard.</font>

371
00:34:52,166 --> 00:34:53,133
<font color="#787878">And lrina.</font>

372
00:34:53,367 --> 00:34:54,334
<font color="#787878">Honey, come here.</font>

373
00:34:56,704 --> 00:34:58,001
<font color="#787878">Why?</font>

374
00:34:58,139 --> 00:34:59,231
<font color="#787878">What did lrina see in the woods?</font>

375
00:34:59,340 --> 00:35:00,637
<font color="#787878">We were just walking.</font>

376
00:35:01,275 --> 00:35:02,867
<font color="#787878">Ness was catching snowflakes.</font>

377
00:35:06,647 --> 00:35:07,875
<font color="#787878">Of course.</font>

