380
00:35:19,694 --> 00:35:20,752
<font color="#787878">So enchanting.</font>

381
00:35:20,928 --> 00:35:22,896
<font color="#787878">To be near them was to love them.</font>

382
00:35:22,997 --> 00:35:25,659
<font color="#787878">But their development was frozen at the age they were turned.</font>

383
