00:36:17,251 --> 00:36:19,219
<font color="#787878">Long-established covens were torn apart.</font>

399
00:36:19,654 --> 00:36:21,781
<font color="#787878">Countless humans slaughtered.</font>

400
00:36:24,325 --> 00:36:26,122
<font color="#787878">Traditions, friends,</font>

